name: 1% Left - Web Version
description:
The browser playable version of 1% left (the same game fitted for web)

Not much power left. You've been down here for a very long time, your inner clock is broken.

Now it's the time to leave this place. You must choose wisely which function you'll use to escape. you can either move, listen or see what's ahead and around.

Good luck

Art: Kenney.nl
